prompt.title: Embedding for Book: AI Workflow Definition
prompt.content: Book, a markdown-based language, allows users to define AI applications by specifying workflows, personas (virtual employees), and knowledge sources.  This simplifies the process of building complex AI pipelines compared to traditional coding.  It features a VSCode plugin for `.book` file support.
